        <mxCell id="131" value="&lt;b&gt;bedrock-runtime&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;com.amazonaws.us-east-1&lt;br&gt;.bedrock-runtime&lt;br&gt;Interface · PrivateDNS: on&lt;br&gt;SG: allow 443 from ECS SG&lt;br&gt;Saves NAT cost for all Bedrock calls"
          style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FF9900;strokeColor=#CC7A00;fontColor=#000000;fontSize=8;"
